  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "A patient rally unfolds here, with both sides battling it out at the kitchen line. The primary player, Daniella, demonstrates excellent control with a series of well-placed dinks. Unfortunately, the rally concludes with an unforced error off an attempted speed-up.",
    "hype_announcer_charged": "WOAH! Look at this kitchen battle! Dinks flying left and right! Daniella is ON FIRE with that touch! But wait... Bill goes for the kill and... OH NO! It's OUT! What a way to end a solid rally!",
