    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, it appears we have a pickleball match. There were some balls hit, and some balls not hit. One player, I believe her name was Daniella, seemed to be quite adept at the dink. The other player, Bill, attempted a shot that, shall we say, went on a brief, unscheduled vacation out of bounds. Stay classy, pickleball fans.",
    "chuck_norris_voice": "Chuck Norris doesn't play pickleball, pickleball plays him. But if it did, he'd win every point with a single stare.",
    "color_commentator_banter": "You know, that's the beauty of pickleball, isn't it? You can have these long, grinding rallies where it's all about finesse and control. Then, BAM! Someone tries to end it and it goes sideways. It's a mental game as much as a physical one.",
    "crowd_chant_if_epic": null,
